        "email": "di.wang@intel.com",
        "username": "wangdi",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2015-11-12 17:39:08.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n\"Also I think that tgt_send_buffer() should take a struct l_wait_info * parameter so that we do not have this problem again.\"\n\nstruct l_wait_info or struct l_wait_info * ? if you mean l_wait_info, then it is big enough to put it into thread_info?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
